(94, 'The Sun Mễ Trì', 'the-sun-me-tri', 24, NULL, 'https://chkvietnam.vn/storage/upload/files/1572853265-Untitled-30.png', '<h2><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">TH&Ocirc;NG TIN CHUNG</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">T&ecirc;n dự &aacute;n</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The Sun Mễ Tr&igrave;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Địa chỉ</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">đường Mễ Tr&igrave;, Phường Mễ Tr&igrave;, Nam Từ Li&ecirc;m, Hà N&ocirc;̣i</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Tổng diện t&iacute;ch</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">2.349 m&sup2;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Mật độ x&acirc;y dựng</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">45%</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Loại h&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t triển</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Căn hộ, Chung cư</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Quy m&ocirc; dự &aacute;n</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">270 căn hộ</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>', '<h2><span style=\"font-size:20px\">