Th&aacute;ng 11/2018&nbsp;<br />\r\n- Thời gian b&agrave;n giao: 2021</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://chkvietnam.vn/storage/upload/files/1566875975-Untitled-1.png\" /></p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 33, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-08-26 20:19:52', '2019-08-26 20:19:52');
